PRAYER FOR RELIEF Wherefore, the Commission respectfully requests that this Court: A. Grant a permanent injunction enjoining Defendant Employer, its officers, successors, assigns and all persons in active concert or participation with it, from engaging in the conduct alleged in paragraph 7 above and any other employment practice which discriminates on the basis of age against individuals 40 years of age and older. Store 409 closed during nighttime hours before May 2002, but starting on or about May 18, 2002, it stayed open for business 24 hours per day. When Store 409 went 24 hours, Tittle, Scobin, and McClusky, and Stacy Warren (“Warren”) worked on Garrison’s night stocking crew. Counce was initially responsible for the entire night crew at Store 409, and he became the Night Assistant Manager when Store 409 went 24 hours in 2002. Wal-Mart has written corporate policies which govern employee
